# Project Initialization Requirements (Repo Baseline)

When initializing this repository (or when bootstrapping a fresh clone), ensure the baseline structure exists:

- `docs/` is present and contains the documentation index (`docs/README.md`).
- `tasks/` is present and contains `tasks/agent-log.md`.
- `CHANGELOG.md` is present at repository root.

If any of these are missing, create them before making substantive changes.

## Governing standards

- Documentation rules: `.cursor/rules/docs-standard.mdc`
- Task tracking + changelog discipline: `.cursor/rules/tasks-plans-changelog.mdc`
